{"word":"G190 - ἀκολουθέω - akolouthéō - ak-ol-oo-theh'-o - Follow","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκολουθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>akolouthéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ak-ol-oo-theh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Follow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பின்செல், பின்பற்று, பின்னே செய், பின்னே போ"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to follow one who precedes, join him as his attendant, accompany him"},{"paragraph":"2. to join one as a disciple, become or be his disciple; side with his party"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a particle of union) and <b>&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x03B8;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>keleuthos</b> (a <i>road</i>); properly to <i>be in the same way with</i>, that is, to <i>accompany</i> (specifically as a disciple): - follow, reach."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1811 - ἐξακολουθέω - exakolouthéō - ex-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o/1811\">G1811</a>, <a href=\"#/G1872 - ἐπακολουθέω - epakolouthéō - ep-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o/1872\">G1872</a>, <a href=\"#/G190 - ἀκολουθέω - akolouthéō - ak-ol-oo-theh'-o/190\">G190</a>, <a href=\"#/G3877 - παρακολουθέω - parakolouthéō - par-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o/3877\">G3877</a>, <a href=\"#/G4870 - συνακολουθέω - synakolouthéō - soon-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o/4870\">G4870</a>"}]}